## Crypto Specification

- Algorithm: AES-256-GCM
- Key derivation: PBKDF2-SHA256, 100,000 iterations minimum
- IV: 12 bytes (96 bits), random per encryption
- Salt: 32 bytes, random per vault
- Auth tag: 16 bytes (128 bits)

